GREAT LAKES:  Partnership signed with AUF=20

The French-speaking University Agency, AUF, and the Economic Community of
the Great Lakes Countries have signed a partnership
http://www.auf.org/communication-information/actualites/glacs2010.html?var=
=3Dlettre_AUF_62
to support higher education and research in the community=92s three member
countries =96 Burundi, the Democratic Republic of Congo and Rwanda.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D20100716193954521

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

DR CONGO: Minister meets donors for reform funds=20

The Democratic Republic of Congo=92s Minister of Higher Education and
Universities Professor L=E9onard Mashako Mamba has met funding agencies and
other partners to present policies and reforms for which the government is
seeking support, reported
http://www.laprosperiteonline.net/show.php?id=3D4935&rubrique=3DNation of
Kinshasa.
Full report on the University World News site:
http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?story=3D201007161938408

