SENEGAL: Students on the rampage =96 again

In the latest of a number of violent demonstrations, students at the
Universit=E9 Cheikh Anta Diop of Dakar went on the rampage this month,
setting fire and causing other damage to university offices, and attacking
the rector and a faculty dean with poison gas, said newspaper reports.=20
